      • branchApp

        public void branchApp(int option)
        Branches the application menu control flow to different sub menus. One case for displaying all doors, one for submitting a new application and one for returning to the main menu.
        Parameters:
        option - boolean, determines which menu to display

      • newApp

        public void newApp()
        Guides user to submit a new application. Once the new application is created, the user will have an option to submit the application or to cancel it. If the user for the request is not found, the application is cancelled.
